All those nifty little things you find, the pieces of info, the newspapers, etc. what has come of them? Nothing.<br>
Take Iksar for example (thanks Zildrax!). You KNOW their plan is to conquer Norrath. That's their back-story. Does Verant bother to tie that in with any other parts of the story though? No. Instead, the Iksar are still on Kunark twiddling their thumbs, and they always will be. This makes it difficult for Iksar RPers to talk about how they'll be the rulers of Norrath when they KNOW nothing is ever going to happen. It lacks continuity. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <br><font color=#A62A2A>- </font><a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie>Firiona Vie</a><font color=#A62A2A> - </font><a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1>Firiona Vie General Chat</a> <font color=#A62A2A> - </font><br><br><br><br>Powered By <a href=http://www.ezboard.com/>ezboard®</a> Ver. 7.0.8<br>Copyright ©1999-2002 ezboard, Inc.<br>Accelerated By <a href=http://www.wbs.com/ezboard.html>JXEL</a></center></body></html>  

